ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project focuses on optimizing Flipkartâ€™s delivery operations by analyzing logistics data using SQL. With increasing order volumes across metros and Tier-2/Tier-3 cities, delivery delays, route inefficiencies, and warehouse bottlenecks significantly impact operational cost and customer satisfaction.

Using relational logistics datasets, this project builds a SQL-driven analytics system to identify inefficiencies, analyze delays, evaluate warehouse and agent performance, and recommend route optimization strategies.

As described in the problem statement 

