Evaluate warehouse and agent productivity.

Build advanced KPIs for operational decision-making.

Provide actionable, data-driven recommendations for logistics improvement.

ğŸ—‚ï¸ Dataset Description

The project uses five structured relational datasets:

Orders Table

Order_ID, Warehouse_ID, Route_ID, Agent_ID

